osad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n畀完黃店攞淘寶貨賣link又話碌兩野冇詳細睇<br />\n<br />\n上面有晒cap圖又唔睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點傾落去呀黃圈發言人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T16:01:50.000Z","msg":"入面原意指稱嘅只有你同我兩個，而且我見到你誤解咗都即刻澄清返，唔明白點解你要堅持我係黃圈發言人。討論區語意不清係常見之事，澄清返就得，你捉住嚟講無咩意義，亦唔會令你嘅論點更強。<br />\n<br />\ncap圖嗰句我嗰陣打緊回覆睇唔到你下面嘅補充，下面亦有加多個comment表示感謝"},{"pid":"f44b87909e3a91c42e007aa43865d178d3153ac0","tid":2512304,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T16:01:55.000Z","msg":"起底樓主係姜濤hater/PR<br />\n<br />\n姜濤周五生日　電車公司安排「姜濤號」往返石塘咀至北角賀壽<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2509240\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2509240</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWUhYrkomnQZdTSbc8WpaDNXUgGC4TXHgzxreLTEkRkaM?filename=Bq1iKvc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBq1iKvc.png&h=f004191d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4256a0bd92fa90780b6f02a310fa571601489dc3","tid":2512304,"uid":209890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79db82614fb930a2a975e8c61268e63c6fb3c112","tid":2512304,"uid":229834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7af3b091e2e6e544f5e40801b719ebdb9701fd87","tid":2512304,"uid":209890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5eff5c54c3e69402708d2c9eac6298077e5efb48","tid":2512304,"uid":229834,"like":9,"dislike":18,"score":-9,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T14:53:11.000Z","msg":"問下「日資」譚仔好過啦<br />\n<br />\n成間舖養嘅大部分staff都係支那人<br />\n<br />\n成班連燈仔咪又係含到雪雪聲<br />\n<br />\n話咩丸龜買咗所以係日資唔計<br />\n<br />\n成班鄉音阿姐代表佢地起碼肯融入<br />\n<br />\n又話啲staff返譚好過啲白𢭃綜援蝗<br />\n<br />\n永遠唔肯接受自己食譚=養支那女人呢個事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T